#! <COMMENT
#!   IDENTIFIER="445"
#!   COMMENT_VALUE="&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;meta charset=&quot;utf-8&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;&#10;p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }&#10;hr { height: 1px; border-width: 0; }&#10;li.unchecked::marker { content: &quot;\2610&quot;; }&#10;li.checked::marker { content: &quot;\2612&quot;; }&#10;&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:&apos;Tahoma&apos;; font-size:9pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;08-10-2025 1e versie derived from webhook versie om er een versie van te maken die 1x per dag alle inspecties van die dag rapporteert.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;....&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;15-11-2025 Inbouwen verwerken dakonderhoud&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;25-11-2025  Statuswijzigingen aanpassen in rapportage. Nu zijn er 3 statussen &apos;Gereed&apos;, &apos;Deels&apos;, &apos;Niet uitvoerbaar&apos;.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;2-12-2025 Status locaties terugzetten als de nieuwste datum van dakonderhoud of deurinspectie langer dan 6 maanden geleden is.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;12-12-2025 Controle gegevens. Door haperende verbinding op de tablets zijn pulldata velden soms leeg. Deze alsnog vullen. Betreft LocatieNaam, LocatieType en AdresLabel.&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot;-qt-paragraph-type:empty; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#10;&lt;p style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;15-01-2026 Status locatie dakonderhoudop Uitvoeren zetten als de laatste dakinspectie van vorig jaar is.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;"
#!   POSITION="-3262.439251514721 701.52561265099871"
